initial roadmap 6/14/25:

1. Complete v1 of app 
* the ux/ui component coded in swift on XCode of some other IDE
* Decide on what database service to use
* Integrate database service and ux/ui
* Users able to type in their drinks/beers and the stats compile
* Users able to add friends
* Leaderboards across friends

2. Complete v2 of app - add AI camera
* Gather dataset
* Train AI camera
* Integrate AI Camera into the app

3. Complete v3 of app - add location services
* Users see how many beers they have at vertain locations - bars, friend's houses, their home
* leaderboards for cities, larger areas

4. Complete v4 of app - rating functionalities/social media
* Users can post pictures with a drink and rate it.
